msgid "Atha kho, bhaggava, sunakkhatto licchaviputto yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "Then Sunakkhatta came to me,"

msgctxt "dn24:27.2"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "bowed, and sat down to one side."

