msgid ""
"‘Nanu tvaṃ, sunakkhatta, acelaṃ kaḷāramaṭṭakaṃ upasaṅkamitvā pañhaṃ apucchi."
msgstr ""
"‘Didn’t you go to see the naked ascetic Kaḷāramaṭṭaka and ask him a question?"

