msgid "Tassa te acelo kaḷāramaṭṭako pañhaṃ puṭṭho na sampāyāsi."
msgstr "But when he couldn’t answer it,"

msgctxt "dn24:27.9"
msgid "Asampāyanto kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātvākāsi."
msgstr "he displayed irritation, hate, and bitterness."

