msgid "Kiṃ pana, bhante, bhagavā arahattassa maccharāyatī’ti?"
msgstr "But sir, are you jealous of perfected ones?’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="23"></a><a class="pts" id="pts3.11"></a>
