msgid ""
"Evaṃvihitakaṃ no tumhe āyasmanto issarakuttaṃ brahmakuttaṃ ācariyakaṃ "
"aggaññaṃ paññapethā’ti."
msgstr ""
"This how you describe in your tradition that the origin of the world came "
"about as created by the Lord God, by Brahmā.’"

