msgid "Te evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr "They say:"

msgctxt "dn24:94.7"
msgid "‘evaṃ kho no, āvuso gotama, sutaṃ, yathevāyasmā gotamo āhā’ti."
msgstr "‘That is what we have heard, Reverend Gotama, just as you say.’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="86"></a>
msgctxt "dn24:95.1"
msgid "Aggaññañcāhaṃ, bhaggava, pajānāmi."
msgstr "Bhaggava, I understand the origin of the world."

