"nibbuti viditā."
msgstr ""
"I understand this, and what goes beyond it. Yet since I do not misapprehend "
"that understanding, I have realized extinguishment within myself. Directly "
"knowing this, the Realized One does not come to ruin."

msgctxt "dn24:110.2"
msgid "Yadabhijānaṃ tathāgato no anayaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="102"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2.21"></a>
msgctxt "dn24:111.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃvādiṃ kho maṃ, bhaggava, evamakkhāyiṃ eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā asatā tucchā "
"musā abhūtena abbhācikkhanti:"
msgstr ""
"Though I speak and explain like this, certain ascetics and brahmins "
"misrepresent me with the false, baseless, lying, untruthful claim:"

msgctxt "dn24:111.2"
msgid "‘viparīto samaṇo gotamo bhikkhavo ca."
msgstr "‘The ascetic Gotama has a distorted perspective, and so have his monks."

msgctxt "dn24:111.3"
msgid "Samaṇo gotamo evamāha—"
msgstr "He says:"

#. VAR: pajānātī’ti → sampajānātīti (s1-3) | sañjānātīti (pts1)
#. VAR: asubhantveva → asubhanteva (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "dn24:111.4"
msgid ""
"yasmiṃ samaye subhaṃ vimokkhaṃ upasampajja viharati, sabbaṃ tasmiṃ samaye "
"asubhantveva pajānātī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When one enters and remains in the liberation of the beautiful, at that "
"time one only perceives what is ugly.’"

msgctxt "dn24:111.5"
msgid "Na kho panāhaṃ, bhaggava, evaṃ vadāmi:"
msgstr "But I don’t say that."

msgctxt "dn24:111.6"
msgid ""
"‘yasmiṃ samaye subhaṃ vimokkhaṃ upasampajja viharati, sabbaṃ tasmiṃ samaye "
"asubhantveva pajānātī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn24:111.7"
msgid "Evañca khvāhaṃ, bhaggava, vadāmi:"
msgstr "I say this:"

msgctxt "dn24:111.8"
msgid ""
"‘yasmiṃ samaye subhaṃ vimokkhaṃ upasampajja viharati, subhantveva tasmiṃ "
"samaye pajānātī’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When one enters and remains in the liberation of the beautiful, at that "
"time one only perceives what is beautiful.’”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="103"></a><a class="pts" id="pts3.35"></a>
msgctxt "dn24:112.1"
msgid ""
"“Te ca, bhante, viparītā, ye bhagavantaṃ viparītato dahanti bhikkhavo ca."
msgstr ""
"“They are the ones with distorted perspective, sir, who regard the Buddha "
"and the mendicants in this way."

msgctxt "dn24:112.2"
msgid "Evaṃpasanno ahaṃ, bhante, bhagavati."
msgstr ""
"Sir, I am quite confident that the Buddha is capable of teaching me so that "
"I can enter and remain in the liberation on the beautiful.”"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn24:112.3"
msgid ""
"Pahoti me bhagavā tathā dhammaṃ desetuṃ, yathā ahaṃ subhaṃ vimokkhaṃ "
"upasampajja vihareyyan”ti."
msgstr " "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="104"></a>
msgctxt "dn24:113.1"
msgid ""
"“Dukkaraṃ kho etaṃ, bhaggava, tayā aññadiṭṭhikena aññakhantikena "
"aññarucikena aññatrāyogena aññatrācariyakena subhaṃ vimokkhaṃ upasampajja "
"viharituṃ."
msgstr ""
"“It’s hard for you to enter and remain in the liberation on the beautiful, "
"since you have a different view, creed, belief, practice, and tradition."

msgctxt "dn24:113.2"
msgid ""
"Iṅgha tvaṃ, bhaggava, yo ca te ayaṃ mayi pasādo, tameva tvaṃ "
"sādhukamanurakkhā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Come now, Bhaggava, carefully nurture the confidence that you have in me.”"

msgctxt "dn24:113.3"
msgid ""
"“Sace taṃ, bhante, mayā dukkaraṃ aññadiṭṭhikena aññakhantikena aññarucikena "
"aññatrāyogena aññatrācariyakena subhaṃ vimokkhaṃ upasampajja viharituṃ."
msgstr ""
"“If it’s hard for me to enter and remain in the liberation on the beautiful, "
"since I have a different view, creed, belief, practice, and tradition,"

msgctxt "dn24:113.4"
msgid ""
"Yo ca me ayaṃ, bhante, bhagavati pasādo, tamevāhaṃ sādhukamanurakkhissāmī”ti."
msgstr "I shall carefully nurture the confidence that I have in the Buddha.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="105"></a>
msgctxt "dn24:114.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "This is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "dn24:114.2"
msgid "Attamano bhaggavagotto paribbājako bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr "Uplifted, the wanderer Bhaggavagotta approved of what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn24:115.1"
msgid "Pāthikasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
